{
  "stem": "26728.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So it was kind of a gentleman's agreement between the airmen that you didn't go after another airman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "If you got him, you got him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he got away, he got away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But with the infantry, it was more-- there was more intense feelings, more viciousness, more-- more you got-- you saw your friends get killed, and saw their bodies laying there, and-- and maybe heard them, the last words they said, things like this.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I could-- even though I asked the major and he as much as told me to shut up and mind me own business, because I wasn't his-- I was just assigned to him as an observer for-- for about-- about a week.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I reported it when I got back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know whatever happened to my report, but I said this-- this is the kind of stuff that's going on down there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's not right because it's going to be one-- our turn one of these days if we get captured by that unit that these two men.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How would you like to have them just chop off your right hand and turn you loose with no tourniquet or nothing in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, I felt real-- real angry at that incident.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And anyhow, I'm getting ahead of myself, I think, or behind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not sure which.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In March we were in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1945.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were at-- we were in Gelnhausen, which is real near Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Frankfurt on Mainz, which I've been back to several times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just love that part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Have a special hotel we stay in there, and-- and the own-- I know the owner.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I mean, we've been there several times.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
